    <item>
      <title>透支费用上限可能会减少加拿大银行的收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/cap-on-overdraft-fees-poised-to-dent-revenue-at-canadian-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周加拿大联邦预算中的一项提案承诺控制银行向客户透支账户收取的费用——此举将为低收入客户提供救济，同时损害贷方的收入，尽管可能影响不大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/cap-on-overdraft-fees-poised-to-dent-revenue-at-canadian-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:24:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行前行长表示弗里兰的预算有损通胀斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/former-bank-of-canada-governor-dodge-says-freeland-budget-hurts-inflation-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行前行长大卫·道奇表示，联邦政府新预算中支出的增加将使央行应对物价上涨的斗争变得更加困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/former-bank-of-canada-governor-dodge-says-freeland-budget-hurts-inflation-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:23:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨表示欧盟领导人将向乌克兰提供更多爱国者系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/eu-to-send-ukraine-seven-more-patriot-missiles-as-allies-step-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着俄罗斯加大对能源基础设施和城市中心的导弹和无人机袭击力度，德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨向其他欧盟领导人施压，要求其向乌克兰派遣更多爱国者防空系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/eu-to-send-ukraine-seven-more-patriot-missiles-as-allies-step-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:55:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏格兰警方在苏格兰民族党资金调查中指控斯特金的丈夫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-police-re-arrest-man-over-scottish-national-party-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前首席大臣尼古拉·斯特金的丈夫在苏格兰民族党财务调查中被警方指控，这一事态发展将使苏格兰执政党在今年英国大选前的关键时刻受到新的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-police-re-arrest-man-over-scottish-national-party-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:04:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗称以色列的威胁可能引发核政策转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-threatens-strike-on-israeli-nuclear-sites-if-it-s-attacked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗一名高级将领表示，如果以色列威胁攻击其核设施，伊朗可能会重新考虑其核政策，这是一个含蓄的警告，称德黑兰可能会竞相开发核武器，因为 4 月 13 日无人机和导弹袭击后，言论持续升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-threatens-strike-on-israeli-nuclear-sites-if-it-s-attacked</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 13:08:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
